title: X-Treme X-Men
description:
By request from the forums.

This torrent contains Marvel Comics&#039; X-Treme X-Men 1 - 46 plus the Savage Land 4 issue mini series and the 2 issue X-Treme X-Men X-Pose.

X-Treme X-men is another in the endless permutations of the successful X-Men franchise. This series ran from July 2001 to June 2004.

I will leave the commentary to the pundits and suffice it to say that this series contained some critically important story lines that echo into the current X-Men story lines.

Thanks to the scanners and the original sources.

Please seed. Please enjoy.
